# Voice-Leading Explorer — environment variables
#
# This app is fully client-side: no API keys, no secrets, no server, no
# database. Everything below is OPTIONAL. Copy this file to `.env` only if
# you want to override a default.

# Where the piano samples are fetched from. Defaults to the Salamander
# grand piano set on the Tone.js CDN. Point this at your own folder of
# samples (served over HTTP) if you want a different instrument by default.
# Files must be named like A1.mp3, C4.mp3, Ds3.mp3, Fs5.mp3, etc.
# VITE_SAMPLE_BASE_URL=https://tonejs.github.io/audio/salamander/
